description:
Service Usage

This service is used by ELP to send security referral related information to the SRS Orchestrator when the account holder has completed and submitted an online eForm 80. The SRS Orchestrator will then send updates to ICSE (via SV295), ISR (via Web Services) and SRS (via SV339v4).
readme:
Service Usage

This service is used by ELP to send security referral related information to the SRS Orchestrator when the account holder has completed and submitted an online eForm 80. The SRS Orchestrator will then send updates to ICSE (via SV295), ISR (via Web Services) and SRS (via SV339v4).
